      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy again. The body has several deep scratches, noticeable rust on the rocker panels, and a large dent in the rear bumper. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly, the transmission slips in second gear, and the interior upholstery is heavily worn with multiple tears. It\u2019s a project car for someone with the tools and time to restore it, as it currently lacks reliable performance and aesthetic appeal.",
