      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents the zenith of automotive preservation. Every detail, from the flawless exterior luster to the pristine, untouched cabin environment, reflects a legacy of exacting care and climate-controlled storage. This is an investment-grade acquisition intended for the most discerning enthusiast who demands uncompromising excellence.",
