      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into excellence with this meticulously maintained masterpiece. This vehicle presents in showroom condition, having spent its life in a climate-controlled garage under the care of a single dedicated owner. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with zero rock chips or imperfections, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and completely free of creasing or bolster wear, still carrying that subtle new-car scent. Every button, switch, and digital interface functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. With exceptionally low mileage and a smooth, responsive drivetrain, this is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that is indistinguishable from new. No accidents, no pets, and no smoking\u2014simply a flawless example for the most discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
